OL,3,CUS military to stay around Iran until
OL,4,C'real agreement' reached, Trump says
OL,6,FTalks with Nato Secretary General Mark
OL,7,FRutte did not appear to calm US
OL,8,FPresident Donald Trump's frustrations,
OL,9,Fas ITV News International Editor Emma
OL,10,FMurphy and US Correspondent Robert
OL,11,FMoore report
OL,13,FUS President Donald Trump has said all
OL,14,FUS ships, aircraft and military
OL,15,Fpersonnel will "remain in place in,
OL,16,Fand around, Iran, until such time as
OL,17,Fthe REAL AGREEMENT reached is fully
OL,18,Fcomplied with".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
