OL,3,CUS military to stay around Iran until
OL,4,C'real agreement' reached, Trump says
OL,6,FWriting on Truth Social overnight,
OL,7,FTrump said the military will stay in
OL,8,Fplace with additional ammunition,
OL,9,Fweaponry, "and anything else that is
OL,10,Fappropriate and necessary for the
OL,11,Flethal prosecution and destruction of
OL,12,Fan already substantially degraded
OL,13,Fenemy".
OL,15,FThe statement comes a day after Trump
OL,16,Fand Iran agreed to a two-week
OL,17,Fceasefire, with negotiations based on
OL,18,Fa 10-point plan proposed by Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
