OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775743871
OL,3,CUS military to stay around Iran until
OL,4,C'real agreement' reached, Trump says
OL,6,FTrump had described the plan as "a
OL,7,Fworkable basis on which to negotiate",
OL,8,Fbut it did include the withdrawal of
OL,9,FUS "combat forces" from the region and
OL,10,FIran being allowed to continue its
OL,11,Furanium enrichment programmes ` both
OL,12,Flikely sticking points in the
OL,13,Fnegotiations.
OL,15,F"Our great Military is Loading Up and
OL,16,FResting, looking forward, actually, to
OL,17,Fits next Conquest. AMERICA IS BACK!",
OL,18,Fhis post concluded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
