OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FTrump's 'frank' meeting with Nato chief
OL,13,FThe US president met with Nato
OL,14,FSecretary General Mark Rutte on
OL,15,FWednesday in what the Dutch politician
OL,16,Fdescribed as a "frank and open
OL,17,Fdiscussion".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775743871
OL,3,CUS military to stay around Iran until
OL,4,C'real agreement' reached, Trump says
OL,6,FRutte highlighted efforts to secure
OL,7,Fthe Strait of Hormuz shipping lane,
OL,8,Fand the role UK Prime Minister Sir
OL,9,FKeir Starmer was playing, but he
OL,10,Facknowledged the US president was
OL,11,F"clearly disappointed" with how
OL,12,FEuropean allies had responded to his
OL,13,Factions in Iran.
OL,15,FThe talks did not appear to calm the
OL,16,Fpresident's frustrations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
