OL,3,CUS military to stay around Iran until
OL,4,C'real agreement' reached, Trump says
OL,6,F"NATO WASN'T THERE WHEN WE NEEDED
OL,7,FTHEM, AND THEY WON'T BE THERE IF WE
OL,8,FNEED THEM AGAIN. REMEMBER GREENLAND,
OL,9,FTHAT BIG, POORLY RUN, PIECE OF
OL,10,FICE!!!", Trump wrote on Truth Social
OL,11,Fshortly after the meeting.
OL,13,FEarlier the White House said Britain
OL,14,Fand other Nato allies had "turned
OL,15,Ftheir backs" on the American people
OL,16,Fduring the war.
OL,18,FHe has previously raised the
OL,19,Fpossibility of the US quitting Nato,
OL,20,Fbranding it a "paper tiger".
