OL,3,CUS military to stay around Iran until
OL,4,C'real agreement' reached, Trump says
OL,6,FThe UK's refusal to be drawn into the
OL,7,Foffensive against Iran, dubbed
OL,8,FOperation Epic Fury by the US, and to
OL,9,Frestrict the use of its bases by
OL,10,FAmerican forces has put a severe
OL,11,Fstrain on relations between Starmer
OL,12,Fand Trump.
OL,14,FTrump has repeatedly criticised and
OL,15,Fmocked the prime minister and the
OL,16,FBritish military, including describing
OL,17,Fthe UK's aircraft carriers as "toys"
OL,18,Fthat "aren't the best".
OL,20,FIsrael's strikes on Lebanon
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
