PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775743871
OL,3,CUS military to stay around Iran until
OL,4,C'real agreement' reached, Trump says
OL,6,FIsrael is part of the two-week
OL,7,Fceasefire arrangement, but President
OL,8,FBenjamin Netanyahu said early on
OL,9,FWednesday that the deal would not
OL,10,Fcover fighting against Hezbollah.
OL,12,FIsraeli strikes hit several dense
OL,13,Fcommercial and residential areas in
OL,14,Fcentral Beirut on Wednesday afternoon
OL,15,Fwithout warning, killing dozens and
OL,16,Fwounding hundreds of people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
