PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775743871
OL,3,CUS military to stay around Iran until
OL,4,C'real agreement' reached, Trump says
OL,6,FThe Israeli military called it the
OL,7,F"largest coordinated strike" in the
OL,8,Fcurrent conflict, striking more than
OL,9,F100 Hezbollah targets within 10
OL,10,Fminutes in Beirut, southern Lebanon
OL,11,Fand the eastern Bekaa valley.
OL,13,FIn unusually strong language, UN
OL,14,FSecretary-General Antonio Guterres
OL,15,F"unequivocally" condemned the strikes,
OL,16,Faccording to a statement by his
OL,17,Fspokesperson, Stephane Dujarric.
OL,19,FIran closed the Strait of Hormuz again
OL,20,Fon Wednesday in response to the
OL,21,Fattacks against the militant group.
