OL,3,CUS military to stay around Iran until
OL,4,C'real agreement' reached, Trump says
OL,6,FIn its 10-point plan, Iran said the US
OL,7,Fmust agree to "cessation of the war on
OL,8,Fall fronts, including against the
OL,9,Fheroic Islamic resistance in Lebanon".
OL,11,FBritish Foreign Secretary Yvette
OL,12,FCooper is expected to say in a speech
OL,13,Fon Thursday evening that Lebanon must
OL,14,Fbe included in the Iran ceasefire
OL,15,Fagreement and that there "must be no
OL,16,Freturn to conflict".
